  "sn27.3:1.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 27",
  "sn27.3:2.1": "1. Kilesavagga",
  "sn27.3:3.1": "3. Viññāṇasutta",
  "sn27.3:4.1": "Sāvatthinidānaṃ.",
  "sn27.3:4.2": "“Yo, bhikkhave, cakkhuviññāṇasmiṃ chandarāgo, cittasseso upakkileso.",
  "sn27.3:4.3": "Yo sotaviññāṇasmiṃ …",
  "sn27.3:4.4": "yo ghānaviññāṇasmiṃ …",
  "sn27.3:4.5": "yo jivhāviññāṇasmiṃ …",
  "sn27.3:4.6": "yo kāyaviññāṇasmiṃ …",
  "sn27.3:4.7": "yo manoviññāṇasmiṃ chandarāgo, cittasseso upakkileso.",
  "sn27.3:4.8": "Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno imesu chasu ṭhānesu cetaso upakkileso pahīno hoti, nekkhammaninnañcassa cittaṃ hoti.",
  "sn27.3:4.9": "Nekkhammaparibhāvitaṃ cittaṃ kammaniyaṃ khāyati, abhiññā sacchikaraṇīyesu dhammesū”ti.",
  "sn27.3:5.1": "Tatiyaṃ."
}